773
00:59:37.870 --> 00:59:39.413 
newcomer actor Lee Chun-oh?

774
00:59:39.830 --> 00:59:40.539 
Who?

775
00:59:40.956 --> 00:59:42.249 
Were you baking.

776
00:59:42.457 --> 00:59:43.458 
and suddenly.

777
00:59:44.126 --> 00:59:46.253 
decided you want Ara all to yourself?

778
